    <title>Converting a document:</title>
    <body>
      <ol>
        <li>Select the type of conversion from the <b>Tools -&gt; Batch Converter</b> submenu.</li>
        <li>Add the <b>Input files</b>.</li>
        <li>Choose the path of the <b>Output folder</b> that will contain the converted document.</li>
        <li>Click the <b>Convert</b> button.</li>
      </ol>
    </body>
